  "original_title": "\u0db4\u0ddc\u0dbd\u0dd2\u0dc3\u0dca \u0d9a\u0ddc\u0da7\u0dca\u0da8\u0dcf\u0dc3 7\u0d9a\u0da7 \u0d87\u0db3\u0dd2\u0dbb\u0dd2 \u0db1\u0dd3\u0dad\u0dd2\u0dba",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Curfew for 7 police divisions",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Police curfew has been imposed on 7 police divisions of Hira province from 9.30 tonight until further notice. Accordingly, police curfew has been imposed on Negombo, Kelaniya, Nugegoda, Mt., Colombo (North), Colombo (South) and Colombo (Central) divisions. have",
        "The announcement of the IGP states that all persons in those police jurisdictions should stay in their homes while considering violation of the police curfew as a hindrance to the maintenance of public order.",
        "The Inspector General of Police further said in the announcement that traveling through the areas where police curfew is in effect is completely prohibited and for that other alternative routes should be used.",
        "Meanwhile, it has been planned to launch protest movements against the existing government tomorrow."
      ],
